============ INSTALLATION ============

1) Install Python3 (Better with 3.6.1 or greater)
2) Install PIP (A package manager for python modules)
    $sudo apt-get install python3-pip
2) Install Pygame : 
    $python3 -m pip install -U pygame --user





















============= FOR DEVELOPPER ==============

To compile python script with all libraries into one file
1) Install pyinstaller
    $ python3 -m pip install pyinstaller
2) $ pyinstaller path/to/script.py